                     <interp inst="t17980418-21-person184" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am the constable of the night. (Produces the petticoat).</p>
               <p>Minet. This is my petticoat, I made it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I never had the petticoat, I know nothing of it.</p>
